	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">These are the sequence of steps in adding opportunities:</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">> Select Company > Select Contacts > Select Opportunity > Define Product Distribution > Define Account Distribution > Select Partner > Select Partner Contacts</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Select Company</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on New Opportunity, select the company via the radio button and click Select</td>
	</tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">If the company is not in the list, enter the company information on this form</td>
	</tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Next, click on New Opportunity, select the company via the radio button and click Select</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Select Contacts</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">4.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">If the customer name (contact) is not in the list, enter the name on this form</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Select Opportunity Type</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">5.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Use the pulldown menu and select the Contact Type Select Opportunity</td>
	</tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">6.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">
			Enter the opportunity details and click on Submit<br>
			Note: Specify the stage of this opportunity:<br>
			<li>10% - Initial Meeting</li>
			<li>25% - Req. Study Done</li>
			<li>50% - Proposal Submitted</li>
			<li>75% - Shortlisted</li>
		</td>
	</tr>
