    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">7.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Specify which product belong to this opportunity, enter the value and click on Submit. The screen will display your product list. If you wish to add more products, use the New Products screen to add. To proceed to the next step, click Next.</td>
